description:
I want to be able to consume the D365 WebAPI Actions

The D365 WebAPI Create Contact Actions can be called using the Microsoft provided guidelines

steps.name: I create a new BasicContact with expected message outcome metadata#contacts(contactid,defra_uniquereference)/$entity

elements.name: Creating a UK - CITIZEN - with ContactInvalidTnCDate

steps.name: I create a new ContactInvalidTnCDate with expected message outcome DateTime is less than minumum value supported by CrmDateTime.

elements.name: Creating a UK - CITIZEN - with DuplicateB2cObjectId

steps.name: I create a new DuplicateB2cObjectId with expected message outcome A record that has the attribute values B2C Object Id already exists.

steps.name: I create a new InvalidB2cObjectId with expected message outcome B2C - Object - ID must be a valid Guid format.

elements.name: Creating a UK - CITIZEN - with ContactWithDuplicateEmail

steps.name: I create a new ContactWithDuplicateEmail with expected message outcome A record that has the attribute values Principal Email Address already exists.

steps.name: I create a new MissingBuildNameNo with expected message outcome Correspondence Address BuildingNumber orBuildingName is required
